                    <div class=""card-body"">
                        <h1 class=""card-title"">E<sub>k </sub>= ½mv<sup>2</sup></h1>
                        <p class=""card-text"">The m still stays the same but v is now increased from 70mph to 100mph.</p>
                        <p class=""card-text"">Mass = 1,600 kilograms </p>
                        <p class=""card-text"">Speed = 100 miles per hour <strong>or</strong> 45 metres per second<sup>2</sup></p>
                        <p class=""card-text"">
                            It's worth working out the squared before putting it into the equation, so
